**MealSwipe: Team Weekly Report (Week 10\)**

| Status Report |
| :---- |

*Write a one-third to one-half page status report describing the team’s overall progress and challenges faced last week. Also discuss the team’s goals and plan for this week.*

During the past week, the team focused on enhancing the MealSwipe application, progressing on several fronts including the ongoing refinement of the filter feature, which requires additional UI improvements and expanded filtering options. Key accomplishments include the successful creation and deployment of the database, as well as integrating trash and liked features into this database, alongside the completion of API testing for the backend. Feedback from stakeholders emphasized the need for a more intuitive user interface and a more effective sorting algorithm, with specific suggestions for improvement. Looking ahead, the team plans to implement Google OAuth, finalize the user interface, and develop a small prototype, with continued efforts to finalize the filtering capabilities.
